metadata.name: Power Trip
metadata.description:
Ideologies are a means to an end.

About the collection:  
Marinette was created during a time of deep personal trauma. Feelings of inadequacies and a lack of control over personal situations compelled me to create a "doll" like figure.  
Her long dark hair is ever present and manipulates her situations, good or bad. Her eyes are intense and mysterious. 
Her figure is exposed. Her feelings are exposed. She is raw and unapologetic. She is Marinette.
